    • Method Detail

      • checkLineFitVersionString

        public static Version.VersionComparisonResult checkLineFitVersionString(java.lang.String version)
        Checks the passed LineFit version number string against the current LineFit version to see if it is the same, newer, or older.
        Parameters:
        version - The string containing the version number as text
        Returns:
        int representing the relationship with negative meaning it is an older version, positive meaning a newer version, and 0 meaning the same version. If the versions are not equal it will return the number that does not match up (i.e. 2 (or -2) if the minor versions do not match)

      • checkLineFitFileFormatVersionString

        public static Version.VersionComparisonResult checkLineFitFileFormatVersionString(java.lang.String fileVersion)
        Checks the passed LineFit FileFormat version number string against the current LineFit File Format version to see if it is the same, newer, or older.
        Parameters:
        fileVersion - The string containing the File Format version number as text
        Returns:
        int representing the relationship with negative meaning it is an older version, positive meaning a newer version, and 0 meaning the same version. If the versions are not equal it will return the number that does not match up (i.e. 2 (or -2) if the minor versions do not match)

      • isLineFitFileVersionBefore

        public static boolean isLineFitFileVersionBefore(java.lang.String toCheck,
                                                 int majorVersion,
                                                 int minorVersion)
        Checks if the passed LineFit file version string is before the version passed in
        Parameters:
        toCheck - The version string to check against the passed values
        majorVersion - The major portion of the version of the version to check if the passed value is before
        minorVersion - The major portion of the version of the version to check if the passed value is before
        Returns:
        True if the version in the string is a earlier version than the one passed in. False if it is the same or a newer version
